dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of various maze configurations created within the DeepMind Lab environment, used for training and testing reinforcement learning agents in navigation tasks. Mazes range in size from 5x5 to 21x21 cells.
dcterms:title: DeepMind Lab Maze Dataset
